{"tid":2507070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫苗施打進度緩慢 彭博抗疫排名台灣下降至第5","createTime":"2021-04-27T18:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T18:18:00.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f783e3c1fae2b51ffbe35871827f39c2612a4d","tid":2507070,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:15:36.000Z","msg":"《彭博社》（Bloomberg）每個月都會公布「全球抗疫韌性排名」（Covid Resilience Ranking），最新的4月份排名，台灣從第4名降到第5名，主要是因為目前台灣的疫苗覆蓋率僅0.1%，接種速度不夠快。<br />\n<br />\n在新排名中，新加坡因為有接近五分之一的人口已經接種疫苗，因此首度擠下紐西蘭登上榜首；而在遏止擴大傳播方面位於前段班的紐西蘭、澳洲、台灣則都處於疫苗接種進度落後的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博社》指出，新加坡因實施邊境管制和嚴格的隔離措施，讓本土病例減少到幾乎為0，民眾日常生活外出沒有受到太大影響，甚至還可以參加演唱會和郵輪旅遊；在疫苗接種的部分，新加坡的疫苗覆蓋率亦達19.4 ％，為亞洲最高。<br />\n<br />\n美國的排名在這個月躍升4位登上第17名，因為疫苗施打進展迅速，死亡人數減少，但同時防疫措施放鬆，確診病例也增加了；而英國在解除封城狀態後，排名上升了7位至第18名，目前正結合快速接種疫苗和更嚴格的邊境管制，以防止新的變種病毒入侵。<br />\n<br />\n疫情幾乎失控、醫療崩潰的印度，因為出現傳染力更強的「雙重突變病毒」和「三重突變病毒」，加上民眾在之前疫情趨緩後，對於防疫措施鬆懈，現在每天新增超過30萬人確診，這個月一口氣下降10位掉到第30名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/564/60768f420b397.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F564%2F60768f420b397.png&h=1a56e320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣現已開放自費接種武肺疫苗。   圖：中央流行疫情指揮中心/提供<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-27/569078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-04-27%2F569078&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=0626d766\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-27/569078</a>"},{"pid":"438b292fe07b29058c522b459b3ab0347f9631b0","tid":2507070,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSBGfGCjEtBHZ7RJMwxtu4uMbEKHzWT8whzkuXNQGEDNg?filename=sGAfftL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGAfftL.png&h=62f02b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港第10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0674b56747b24e748624147a3f49e257edbd6499","tid":2507070,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"The Covid Resilience Ranking<br />\n<br />\nThe Best and Worst Places to Be as Variants Outrace Vaccinations<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/covid-resilience-ranking/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fgraphics%2Fcovid-resilience-ranking%2F&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0mVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=eee8f556\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/covid-resilience-ranking/</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"438b292fe07b29058c522b459b3ab0347f9631b0","tid":2507070,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T18:17:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGAfftL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGAfftL.png&h=62f02b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港第10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}